      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong claim. My team is pretty skeptical because we've had issues with other brands claiming \"all-day\" battery but actually dying around the 16 or 18-hour mark when the load is actually high. Do you have any specific test data or technical documentation you can share that shows them hitting that full 24-hour mark under heavy drilling conditions? I need to justify this to my boss.",
